<h1>Roadmap</h1><% @title_text = 'Roadmap' %>

<p>
  This document is meant to share some plans on the further project development.
  There will be no dates, at least so far, just priorities and order of the milestones.
</p>

<dl class="roadmap">
  <dt>RightJS UI: Slider</dt>
  <ul>
    <li>Standard slider widget</li>
  </ul>
  
  <dt>RightJS UI: Rater</dt>
  <ul>
    <li>Standard rating (with stars) widget</li>
  </ul>
  
  <dt>RightJS UI: Voter</dt>
  <ul>
    <li>Standard voting (up/down) widget</li>
  </ul>
  
  <dt>RightJS UI: Selectboxes</dt>
  <ul>
    <li>Vitual selectboxes widget</li>
  </ul>
  
  <dt>RightJS Goods: Validators</dt>
  <ul>
    <li>Automatic form validators plugin</li>
  </ul>
  
  <dt>RightJS Home: Russian Documentation</dt>
  <ul>
    <li>Multi-lingual support for the official site</li>
    <li>Core and Tutorials translation in Russian</li>
  </ul>
  
  <dt>RightJS UI: RRRRTE</dt>
  <ul>
    <li>Simple RightJS based RTE, using a 'contenteditable' field</li>
  </ul>
  
  <dt>RightJS Core: Version 1.5</dt>
  <ul>
    <li>Split the core by browser support. Core, olds and IE modules</li>
    <li>Browser specific builds</li>
    <li>Ongoing optimizations</li>
    <li>New features</li>
  </ul>
  
  <dt>RightJS Goods: More Visual Effects</dt>
  <ul>
    <li>More visual effects for the additional effects collection</li>
  </ul>
</dl>